uk.co.codera.lang.concurrent

Class TaskCallbackAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.co.codera.lang.concurrent.TaskCallbackAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TaskCallback

    public class TaskCallbackAdapter
extends Object
implements TaskCallback

    Implementation of the TaskCallback where all the methods have a do nothing implementation.

    Rather than implement the interface directly clients should extend this class and override behaviour as necessary. This will ensure that if methods are added to the interface in the future client code will still compile as a do nothing implementation will be added to this class.

    Author:
    andystewart
